0populace.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThese%20are%20the%20investment%20clubs%2C%20a%20common%20fixture%20among%20Singapore's%20three%20major%20universities%20%E2%80%94%20the%20National%20University%20of%20Singapore%20(NUS)%2C%20Singapore%20Management%20University%20(SMU)%2C%20and%20Nanyang%20Technological%20University.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMembers%20of%20these%20clubs%20attend%20training%20sessions%2C%20covering%20topics%20like%20financial%20modeling%20and%20stock%20pitching.%20These%20sessions%20are%20usually%20taught%20by%20senior%20members.%20Club%20alumni%20and%20industry%20professionals%20also%20drop%20in%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eto%20give%20talks%20to%20members.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECompetition%20to%20join%20these%20clubs%20can%20be%20almost%20as%20intense%20as%20attempting%20to%20secure%20a%20top%20job%20with%20bulge%20bracket%20banks%20and%20investment%20firms.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStudent%20leaders%20at%20the%20SMU-Student%20Managed%20Investment%20Fund%20(SMU-SMIF)%20and%20its%20equivalent%20at%20the%20NUS%2C%20the%20NUS%20Investment%20Society%2C%20say%20they've%20seen%20an%20uptick%20in%20applicants%20over%20the%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOver%20200%20people%20per%20batch%20apply%20for%20a%20limited%20number%20of%20seats%2C%20said%20Matthew%20Quek%2C%2025%2C%20who%20joined%20SMU-SMIF%20in%202022%20and%20is%20now%20the%20club's%20vice%20president.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHistorically%2C%20we%20have%20taken%20around%2020%20applicants%2C%26quot%3B%20Quek%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20recent%20years%2C%20we%20have%20upped%20our%20intake.%20Our%20latest%20batch%20has%2024%20members%2C%20the%20largest%20we%20have%20had%20so%20far%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20students%20Business%20Insider%20spoke%20to%20said%20that%20joining%20clubs%20like%20SMU-SMIF%20and%20NUS%20Investment%20Society%20provided%20them%20with%20a%20platform%20to%20brush%20up%20their%20technical%20skills%20and%20build%20connections%20with%20the%20industry.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22e807cfb7-abd0-4c6f-be07-2a63415fff6c%5C%22%3ETechnical%20know-how%20and%20hands-on%20experiences%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EShannon%20Chong%2C%2021%2C%20is%20a%20junior%20at%20SMU.%20The%20accountancy%20undergraduate%20said%20her%20budding%20interest%20in%20finance%20was%20what%20drew%20her%20to%20the%20SMU-SMIF.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EChong%20said%20she%20was%2017%20when%20she%20realized%20she%20wanted%20a%20career%20in%20finance%20after%20participating%20in%20a%20high%20school%20case%20competition%20organized%20by%20Tiger%20Global%20Management%2C%20an%20investment%20firm.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20found%20the%20mix%20of%20qualitative%20and%20quantitative%20analysis%20rather%20interesting.%20I%20also%20enjoyed%20getting%20to%20look%20at%20different%20business%20models%2C%26quot%3B%20Chong%20said%20of%20her%20experience%20with%20the%20case%20competition.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EChong%20said%20she%20wanted%20a%20hands-on%20learning%20experience.%20That's%20when%20she%20heard%20from%20her%20seniors%20that%20SMIF%20was%20a%20way%20to%20get%20training%20outside%20the%20classroom.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%227008%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Shannon%20Chong%20presenting%20her%20stock%20pitch%20at%20the%20Point72%20x%20Nanyang%20Capital%20Stock%20Pitch%20Challenge.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F680b30243fe8d39283640aa1%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224672%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EShannon%20Chong%20(left)%2C%2022%2C%20joined%20SMU-SMIF%20as%20a%20freshman%20in%202022.%20She%20currently%20serves%20as%20the%20club's%20president.%3Cp%3EShannon%20Chong%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSMIF%20has%20provided%20me%20with%20the%20training%2C%20not%20only%20in%20terms%20of%20the%20technical%20deck%20making%20and%20financial%20modeling%20skills%2C%20but%20also%20in%20terms%20of%20soft%20skills%20like%20critical%20thinking%20and%20communication%2C%26quot%3B%20Chong%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EChong%20started%20out%20as%20a%20junior%20analyst%20for%20the%20club%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ein%20her%20freshman%20year%2C%20before%20climbing%20the%20ranks%20and%20taking%20over%20as%20club%20president%20in%20August.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EChong%20has%20completed%20two%20internships%2C%20one%20in%20investment%20banking%20and%20the%20other%20on%20the%20buy-side.%20She%20told%20BI%20that%20former%20SMU-SMIF%20members%20and%20seniors%20also%20gave%20her%20advice%20and%20provided%20referrals%20when%20she%20was%20applying%20for%20those%20positions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EQuek%2C%20who%20joined%20SMU-SMIF%20in%20the%20same%20year%20as%20Chong%2C%20said%20the%20technical%20skills%20he%20picked%20up%20were%20helpful%20when%20he%20undertook%20buy-side%20and%20sell-side%20internships.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMy%20first%20internship%20was%20with%20a%20public%20equities%20firm%2C%20so%20just%20mainly%20investing%20in%20US%20stocks.%20As%20part%20of%20SMIF%2C%20you%20look%20at%20all%20different%20kinds%20of%20stocks%20from%20the%20US%2C%20from%20Europe.%20So%20for%20that%20internship%2C%20I%20benefited%20a%20lot%20from%20having%20the%20SMIF%20training%2C%26quot%3B%20Quek%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22969759cb-1383-4ed8-a9a6-cc7b9e17cac1%5C%22%3EClubs%20give%20college%20students%20easy%20access%20to%20a%20network%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EYumo%20Pan%2C%2024%2C%20is%20a%20senior%20from%20the%20NUS%20majoring%20in%20quantitative%20finance.%20Pan%20joined%20the%20NUS%20Investment%20Society%20in%20her%20sophomore%20year%20and%20is%20now%20its%20president.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPan%20told%20BI%20that%20joining%20the%20club%20allowed%20her%20to%20gain%20practical%20skills%2C%20like%20how%20to%20pitch%20a%20trading%20idea.%20She%20added%20that%20while%20it%20is%20possible%20for%20students%20to%20break%20into%20the%20finance%20industry%20by%20self-studying%20and%20networking%20aggressively%2C%20joining%20a%20club%20like%20NUS%20Investment%20Society%20will%20help%20students%20to%20get%20a%20leg%20up%20over%20the%20competit