%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EChris%20Hwang%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20cofounder%20of%20The%20Golden%20Duck.%20At%2023%2C%20I%20dropped%20out%20of%20law%20school%20to%20start%20the%20snack%20brand%2C%20which%2C%20a%20decade%20later%2C%20is%20now%20sold%20in%20over%203%2C000%20stores%20worldwide.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Golden%20Duck%20is%20a%20gourmet%20snack%20brand%20that%20reimagines%20Asian%20flavors%20like%20salted%20egg%20yolk.%20Our%20vision%20has%20always%20been%20to%20be%20the%20Ben%20%26amp%3B%20Jerry's%20of%20snacks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20composite%20image%20of%20some%20of%20The%20Golden%20Duck's%20snacks.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67a0777a7bb3f854015b78a8%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22768%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Golden%20Duck%20prides%20itself%20on%20reimagining%20Asian%20flavors%20in%20the%20form%20of%20fun%20snacks.%3Cp%3EThe%20Golden%20Duck%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20started%20small.%20In%202015%2C%20we%20launched%20with%20just%20one%20product%20%E2%80%94%20salted%20egg%20yolk%20chips.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20start%2C%20our%20capacity%20was%20so%20limited%20that%20we%20made%20the%20products%20in%20a%20home%20kitchen.%20As%20a%20result%2C%20we%20could%20only%20make%20about%2050%20packs%20of%20chips%20a%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20it%20started%20getting%20more%20popular%20in%20Singapore%2C%20we%20scaled%20up%20the%20business.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAdding%20staff%2C%20maintaining%20quality%2C%20and%20controlling%20the%20processes%20when%20we%20scaled%20up%20were%20some%20of%20the%20most%20challenging%20parts%20of%20our%20journey.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe've%20also%20weathered%20many%20storms.%20The%20pandemic%20was%20a%20very%20bad%20time%20for%20the%20business%2C%20and%20all%20our%20tourism%20revenue%20evaporated%20overnight.%20We%20had%20to%20reduce%20our%20workforce%20from%20200%20to%20120%2C%20and%20tell%20friends%20we'd%20brought%20on%20board%20that%20we%20won't%20be%20able%20to%20work%20together%20anymore.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFrom%20my%2010%20years%20of%20experience%20running%20The%20Golden%20Duck%2C%20here%20are%20five%20pieces%20of%20advice%20I'd%20give%20to%20anyone%20thinking%20about%20starting%20a%20new%20brand.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22dff7828b-d187-40dd-9f51-44390bf38a9f%5C%22%3E1.%20Get%20started%20and%20test%20cheap%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you're%20thinking%20about%20it%20and%20you've%20not%20yet%2C%20just%20get%20started.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYou%20don't%20have%20to%20quit%20your%20job.%20You%20can%20do%20something%20on%20the%20weekends%2C%20but%20start%20building%20a%20road%20map.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENothing%20is%20stopping%20you%20from%20testing%20it%20right%20now.%20You%20don't%20have%20to%20spend%20thousands%20or%20tens%20of%20thousands%20of%20dollars%20building%20things%2C%20especially%20in%20the%20age%20of%20AI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20if%20you%20have%20a%20dream%2C%20just%20get%20started.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYou%20might%20fail%20at%20first.%20This%20is%20actually%20my%20fifth%20startup%2C%20but%20the%20failures%20gave%20me%20the%20fire%20to%20keep%20putting%20my%20back%20into%20it%20and%20working%20crazy%20hours.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20when%20you%20start%2C%20test%20with%20as%20little%20capital%20as%20possible.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20seen%20people%20start%20businesses%20with%20%245%2C000%20and%20rake%20in%20multimillion-dollar%20revenues%20now.%20I've%20seen%20people%20start%20businesses%20broke%2C%20and%20some%20have%20scaled%20up%20enormously.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20think%20people%20don't%20do%20this%20enough.%20You%20don't%20have%20to%20spend%20a%20lot%20of%20money%20to%20test%20a%20business%20idea.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22f490b18d-eff6-4160-8d24-7518f76ff194%5C%22%3E2.%20Know%20your%20customer%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EReally%20get%20to%20know%20your%20customer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFall%20in%20love%20with%20them%2C%20give%20them%20a%20name%2C%20know%20where%20they%20stay%2C%20have%20a%20whole%20idea%20about%20how%20they%20spend%20their%20budgets%2C%20and%20what%20things%20they%20care%20about%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20this%20method%2C%20we%20found%20success%20in%20Singapore%2C%20Hong%20Kong%2C%20and%20a%20few%20other%20markets.%20However%2C%20to%20scale%20this%20globally%2C%20we%20need%20to%20identify%20this%20customer%20so%20we%20can%20speak%20to%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOur%20target%20customer%20is%2030%20years%20old.%20She%20doesn't%20need%20to%20drive%20a%20car%2C%20but%20some%20of%20them%20do.%20She%20lives%2015%20minutes%20out%20from%20downtown%20Singapore.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20loves%20her%20food.%20She%20is%20very%20active%20on%20social%20media%2C%20whether%20it's%20Instagram%20or%20TikTok%2C%20and%20she%20loves%20sharing%20the%20best%20bits%20of%20her%20food%20journeys.%20She%20has%20big%20dreams.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYou%20need%20to%20be%20specific%20about%20who%20your%20customers%20are%20to%20market%20effectively%20to%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2260a93c00-e6f8-4c89-a6ab-5ce383938050%5C%22%3E3.%20Innovate%20for%20your%20customer%2C%20not%20yourself%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EYou%20have%20to%20innovate%20for%20what%20your%20consumer%20wants%2C%20not%20what%20you%20want.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20love%20snacking.%20Often%2C%20I%20am%20my%20customer%2C%20but%20not%20always.%20Do%20I%20have%20the%20same%20taste%20buds%20as%20the%20Italians%3F%20Or%20the%20French%3F%20I%20don't.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20I%20need%20to%20recognize%20that.%20So%2C%20if%20I%20go%20to%20those%20markets%20and%20try%20those%20products%20and%20see%20what%20their%20best%20sellers%20are%2C%20I%20know%20what%20I'm%20going%20after.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThen%20my%20challenge%20is%2C%20can%20I%20make%20my%20product%20better%20for%20you%2C%20not%20better%20for%20me%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22bccef8cd-18e1-44e4-85ea-d9d5cf216245%5C%22%3E4.%20Today%2C%20authenticity%20is%20king%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EPeople%20all%20around%20the%20world%20are%20creating%20authentic%20experiences.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20all%20know%20what%20sour%20cream%20and%20onion%20taste%20like%2C%20and%20we%20all%20know%20what%20barbecue%20tastes%20like.%20But%20why%20not%20have%20sour%20cream%20and%20Sriracha%2C%20one%20of%20our%20newest%20flavors%20in%20the%20canister%20line%20of%20chips%20that%20we%20launched%20in%202024%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBy%20now%2C%20everybody%20knows%20what%20truffle%20flavor%20is%2C%20but%20why%20not%20have%20truffle%20wagyu%3F%20Again%2C%20that's%20one%20of%20the%20flavors%20that%20we%20launched.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20I%20see%20a%20trend%20that%20people%20are%20looking%20not%20just%20for%20interesting%20one-off%20experiences.%20They're%20looking%20for%20interesting%20new%20staples.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20I%20think%20there's%20a%20very%20strong%20case%20for%20not%20just%20Asian%20flavors%20but%20all%20flavors%20from%20around%20the%20world.%20There's%20a%20huge%20opportunity%20there.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%221b2cfa94-868b-4315-b0f2-5e5742df3ba6%5C%22%3E5.%20Fail%20small%2C%20rectify%20fast%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20know%20that%20many%20entrepreneurs%20have%20shared%20the%20advice%20of%20failing%20small%2C%20so%20I'm%20not%20going%20to%20beat%20that%20drum%20anymore.%20I%20think%20everyone%20knows%20what%20it%20means.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20rectifying%20after%20the%20failure%20is%20super%20important.%20So%20you%20fail%20small%2C%20and%20then%20what%3F%20Do%20you%20just%20sit%20there%20and%20say%2C%20%26quot%3BIt%20didn't%20work%3F%26quot%3B%20No.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEntrepreneurship%20is%20all%20about%20evolution.%20Most%20businesses%20don't%20find%20their%20niche%20until%20a%20good%20one%20to%20two%20years%20in.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20means%20you%20have%20to%20iterate.%20OK%20%E2%80%94%20maybe%20your%20customer%20doesn't%20like%20it%20this%20way.%20Perhaps%20they%20like%20it%20with%20a%20little%20bit%20more%20salt.%20Maybe%20they%20don't%20like%20chips.%20Maybe%20they%20want%20a%20packet%20of%20potato%20wedges%20instead%20of%20chips.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20don't%20rectify%20after%20each%20of%20those%20small%20failures%2C%20then%20you're%20just%20going%20to%20call%20it%20quits%20too%20early.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBecause%20entrepreneurship%20is%20like%20life.%20It's%20all%20about%20evolving%2C%20changing%2C%20and%20growing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdropped-out-of-law-school-start-snack-brand-entrepreneurship-advice-2025-2%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1745799481000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67a06b8d7bb3f854015b787f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdropped-out-of-law-school-start-snack-brand-entrepreneurship-advice-2025-2%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Chris%20Hwang%20dropped%20out%20of%20law%20school%20to%20build%20The%20Golden%20Duck.%20From%20testing%20cheap%20to%20innovating%20for%20the%20customer%2C%20here's%20his%20advice%20for%20entrepreneurs.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22abharade%40insider.com%20(Aditi%20Bharade)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A39%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdropped-out-of-law-school-start-snack-brand-entrepreneurship-advice-2025-2%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Pakistan%20on%20verge%20of%20split%2C%20Balochistan%20will%20be%20a%20new%20nation%3A%20Goa%20CM%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1745799366000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-120679911%2Cimgsize-474289.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Fpakistan-on-verge-of-split-balochistan-will-be-a-new-nation-goa-cm-pramod-sawant%2Farticleshow%2F120679852.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Goa%20CM%20Pramod%20Sawant%20predicted%20the%20potential%20split%20of%20Pakistan%20due%20to%20Balochistan's%20independence%20push%2C%20assuring%20BJP%20workers%20of%20PM%20Modi's%20retaliation%20for%20t