usinessinsider.com%2Ftrump-liberation-day-tariffs-reactions-commentators-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eeconomists%20have%20critiqued%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20administration's%20trade%20strategy%2C%20questioning%20Trump's%20dramatic%20and%20unpredictable%20approach.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETrump%20has%20implemented%20a%20145%25%20tariff%20rate%20on%20Chinese%20goods%2C%20causing%20Beijing%20to%20respond%20by%20placing%20125%25%20tariffs%20on%20US%20goods%20%E2%80%94%20a%20severe%20economic%20escalation%20between%20the%20two%20global%20superpowers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20Bessent%20on%20Sunday%20said%20he%20believes%20there's%20a%20%26quot%3Bpath%26quot%3B%20to%20resolve%20the%20trade%20dispute%20with%20China.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20first%20path%20will%20be%20a%20de-escalation%2C%20which%20I%20think%20the%20Chinese%20are%20going%20to%20have%20to%20have%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20trade%20deal%20can%20take%20months%2C%20but%20an%20agreement%20in%20principle%20and%20the%20good%20behavior%20and%20staying%20within%20the%20parameters%20of%20the%20deal%20by%20our%20trading%20partners%20can%20keep%20the%20tariffs%20from%20ratcheting%20back%20to%20the%20maximum%20level.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fscott-bessent-trump-tariffs-trade-strategic-uncertainty-2025-4%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1745779595000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F680e74613fe8d39283643068%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fscott-bessent-trump-tariffs-trade-strategic-uncertainty-2025-4%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Scott%20Bessent%20told%20ABC%20News%20on%20Sunday%20that%20some%20of%20the%20countries%20looking%20to%20negotiate%20with%20Trump%20should%20curb%20their%20%26quot%3Bnon-tariff%20trade%20barriers.%26quot%3B%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(John%20L