%20to%20buy%20their%20shares%20and%20keep%20the%20place.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20issue%20is%20that%20I've%20offered%20them%20the%20appraisal%20value%2C%20and%20they%20feel%20like%20in%20our%20area%2C%20in%20this%20market%2C%20they%20could%20make%20substantially%20more%20than%20that.%20They're%20insisting%20on%20giving%20me%20a%20third%20of%20the%20land%20(not%20the%20part%20with%20the%20house%20on%20it)%2C%20and%20taking%20offers%20on%20the%20rest.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBesides%20my%20dream%20of%20having%20a%20farm%20someday%2C%20I%20know%20my%20parents%20would%20have%20wanted%20us%20to%20keep%20the%20land.%20How%20do%20I%20get%20my%20brothers%20to%20see%20reason%20and%20to%20do%20the%20right%20thing%20by%20me%20and%20our%20parents'%20memory%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESincerely%2C%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ETrying%20to%20Keep%20It%20in%20the%20Family%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDear%20Trying%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDividing%20an%20inheritance%20tends%20to%20be%20more%20complicated%20than%20it%20may%20seem%20from%20the%20outset.%20We%20want%20to%20believe%20that%20our%20sibling%20relationships%20will%20be%20strong%20enough%20to%20handle%20something%20as%20temporary%20and%20materialistic%20as%20the%20dissemination%20of%20the%20family%20fortune.%20But%20even%20if%20you%20avoid%20any%20lasting%20damage%2C%20you%20often%20still%20hit%20a%20few%20speed%20bumps.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20have%20five%20siblings.%20We%20all%20grew%20up%20in%20the%20same%20house%20with%20the%20same%20parents%2C%20so%20you%20might%20think%20we%20all%20have%20the%20same%20basic%20value%20system.%20Sometimes%20we%20do%2C%20and%20sometimes%20we%20don't.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20instance%2C%20some%20of%20us%20see%20holiday%20gatherings%20as%20something%20akin%20to%20a%20natural%20phenomenon%20%E2%80%94%20if%20you're%20breathing%2C%20you%20make%20it%20work.%20Some%20of%20my%20siblings%20don't%20see%20it%20that%20way.%20They%20believe%20family%20should%20offer%20unconditional%20flexibility%20and%20grace.%20You%20probably%20picked%20up%20from%20my%20pronoun%20usage%20that%20I%20land%20in%20the%20former%20school%20of%20thought.%20This%20doesn't%20mean%20my%20other%20siblings%20are%20wrong%3B%20their%20perspective%20is%20as%20valid%20as%20mine.%20It's%20just%20different.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20tell%20you%20all%20this%20because%20working%20the%20land%20and%20preserving%20your%20parents'%20property%20as%20a%20family%20legacy%20is%20a%20beautiful%20value%20to%20hold%2C%20but%20that%20doesn't%20make%20your%20brothers%20wrong%20for%20not%20sharing%20it.%20Your%20parents%20didn't%20put%20a%20no-sell%20clause%20in%20their%20will%2C%20so%20there's%20no%20reason%20to%20see%20your%20brothers'%20desire%20to%20sell%20as%20a%20betrayal%20of%20your%20parents'%20memories.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20said%2C%20your%20perspective%20is%20also%20valid.%20As%20the%20outdoorsy%20sibling%2C%20it%20would%20make%20sense%20that%20you%20may%20have%20spent%20more%20time%20with%20your%20parents%20out%20on%20the%20land%2C%20watching%20them%20work%2C%20and%20hearing%20them%20dream%20about%20the%20future%20of%20the%20family%20and%20home%20they%20built.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20don't%20say%20this%20to%20dissuade%20you%20from%20fighting%20for%20the%20property.%20I%20think%20you%20should.%20I%20only%20point%20out%20the%20validity%20of%20various%20perspectives%20and%20priorities%20because%20I%20know%20how%20natural%20it%20feels%20to%20attach%20value%20judgments%20to%20personal%20conviction%2C%20and%20those%20are%20the%20fuel%20of%20most%20family%20feuds.%20You%20can%20push%20to%20get%20your%20way%2C%20buy%20out%20your%20siblings%2C%20and%20keep%20your%20parents'%20land%20together%20without%20causing%20an%20irreparable%20rift%20between%20you%20and%20your%20brothers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFirst%2C%20you%20should%20have%20the%20entire%20property%20surveyed%20and%20appraised.%20You%20mentioned%20your%20brothers%20wanting%20to%20give%20you%20a%20third%