%3B%20she%20told%20us.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20means%20an%20owner%20on%20a%20tight%20budget%20can%20start%20with%20the%20base%20truck%2C%20which%20has%20crank%20windows%20and%20no%20radio%2C%20and%20steadily%20upgrade%20and%20personalize%20the%20vehicle%20over%20time%20with%20different%20color%20wraps%20or%20upgraded%20infotainment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere's%20even%20a%20kit%20that%20transforms%20the%20truck%20into%20a%20five-passenger%20SUV.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225935%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20Slate%20EV%20pickup%20that's%20been%20converted%20to%20an%20SUV.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F680be9e53fe8d3928364244c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223957%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20Slate%20EV%20pickup%20with%20off-road%20tires%20converted%20to%20an%20SUV%20with%20the%20door%20removed.%3Cp%3ESlate%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20wide%20array%20of%20accessories%20allows%20the%20Slate%20EV%20to%20grow%20and%20evolve%20with%20its%20owner's%20needs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20may%20be%2C%20they%20were%20single%20when%20they%20first%20purchased%20the%20truck%2C%20and%20they%20recently%20got%20married%2C%20and%20a%20few%20years%20later%2C%20they%20have%2C%20a%20family%2C%20and%20instead%20of%20having%20to%20exchange%20it%20out%20for%20a%20completely%20new%20vehicle%2C%20they%20can%20convert%20it%20into%20a%20five%20passenger%20SUV%20and%20continue%20to%20use%20the%20vehicle%2C%26quot%3B%20Barman%20explained.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20saves%20the%20consumer%20from%20having%20to%20sell%20or%20trade%20in%20a%20paid-for%20vehicle%20and%20generates%20additional%20revenue%20for%20Slate%20from%20a%20single%20sale.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22dfcb6d2b-7e69-4290-9221-b93a0dd483ab%5C%22%3ESlate%20built%20the%20DIY%20EV%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20vehicles%20become%20increasingly%20complex%20and%20expensive%2C%20Slate%20is%20becoming%20a%20rarity%20as%20one%20of%20the%20few%20manufacturers%20encouraging%20owners%20to%20work%20on%20their%20cars.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20it%20plans%20to%20deploy%20a%20direct%20sales%20model%2C%20it%20doesn't%20have%20to%20worry%20about%20sustaining%20a%20network%20of%20dealers%20who%20depend%20on%20their%20service%20departments%20to%20make%20ends%20meet.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225935%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20rendering%20of%20a%20customized%20Slate%20EV%20pickup%20truck%20in%20gray%20and%20red.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F680aa0d4c6ad288d147f1883%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223957%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20customized%20Slate%20EV%20pickup%20truck.%3Cp%3ESlate%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Slate's%20CEO%2C%20upgrade%20work%20on%20its%20vehicles%20is%20designed%20to%20be%20easily%20enough%20for%20owners%20to%20do%20themselves%2C%20and%20the%20company%20plans%20to%20offer%20instructional%20videos%20called%20%26quot%3BSlate%20University%26quot%3B%20to%20guide%20them%20through%20the%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20includes%20series%20hardware%20installs%20like%20adding%20power%20windows%20and%20even%20the%20SUV%20Kit%2C%20including%20rear%20seats%2C%20a%20roll%20cage%2C%20and%20airbags.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlthough%20the%20company%20plans%20to%20have%20local%20partner%20facilities%20that%20can%20do%20the%20work%20professionally%20if%20the%20owner%20isn't%20up%20to%20doing%20the%20wrenching%20themselves.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Slate%20truck%2C%20which%20is%20expected%20to%20be%20built%20in%20an%20as-yet-unnamed%20facility%20in%20the%20Midwestern%20US%2C%20will%20begin%20customer%20deliveries%20at%20the%20end%20of%202026%2C%20the%20company%20says.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20would%20like%20to%20see%20what%20we%20can%20do%20to%20go%20into%20an%20existing%20facility%20that%20has%20been%20shuttered%20and%20reindustrialize%20and%20revitalize%20that%20community%2C%26quot%3B%20Barman%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EReservations%20are%2