s%20also%20unclear%20whether%20there%20are%20more%20detailed%20underlying%20agreements%20that%20spell%20out%20each%20firm's%20responsibilities.%20If%20any%20firm%20challenges%20the%20Trump%20administration%20in%20court%20or%20picks%20up%20a%20client%20Trump%20objects%20to%2C%20he%20could%20issue%20a%20new%20executive%20order.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20he%20has%20a%20different%20interpretation%20than%20the%20firms%2C%20he%20can%20bring%20them%20in%20line%20by%20issuing%20an%20executive%20order%2C%26quot%3B%20Nate%20Eimer%2C%20an%20attorney%20representing%20over%20800%20firms%20opposing%20the%20executive%20orders%2C%20said%20of%20Trump.%20Firms%20that%20settled%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3Bput%20themselves%20in%20a%20very%2C%20very%20difficult%20position.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20White%20House%20has%20not%20answered%20questions%20about%20whether%20nonpublic%20agreements%20exist.%20None%20of%20the%20firms%20that%20made%20deals%20responded%20to%20requests%20for%20comment.%20Representatives%20for%20WilmerHale%20declined%20to%20comment.%20Perkins%20Coie%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20requests%20for%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETrump%20has%20openly%20mused%20about%20using%20the%20law%20firms%20for%20various%20purposes.%20In%20a%20televised%20Cabinet%20meeting%20a%20week%20after%20he%20announced%20sweeping%20tariffs%2C%20he%20said%20they%20could%20negotiate%20trade%20deals.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMike%20Howell%2C%20who%20runs%20The%20Oversight%20Project%2C%20a%20group%20spun%20out%20of%20the%20conservative%20Heritage%20Foundation%2C%20sent%20letters%20to%20many%20law%20firms%20%E2%80%94%20including%20some%20Trump%20hasn't%20targeted%20%E2%80%94%20asking%20them%20to%20devote%20%2410%20million%20worth%20of%20time%20to%20help%20litigate%20freedom%20of%20information%20lawsuits%20against%20agencies%20in%20%26quot%3Bblue%20states.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'm%20dealing%20at%20my%20level%20with%20the%20managing%20partners%2C%20some%20of%20whom%20have%20responded%20ver